        If there are no Shoppinglist above this one the value will be ListUtils.FIRST_ITEM

        important if you are using ListManager other shoppinglists will have their previous_id, modified e.t.c. updated to reflect any changes to this Shoppinglist, but if you do not use the ListManager you must update all other Shoppinglist that may be accefted by these changes

        public org.json.JSONObject getMeta()
        Deprecated. 
        Get the meta information for this Shoppinglist.

        Meta doesn't currently have any restrictions other that it must be a JSONObject, what goes inside is completely up to you.

        What being said, please ensure not to accidentally override any keys that others may have set on the object. This can be done by name spacing your keys. Currently ShopGun are using the eta_ name space for our keys.
